text: M1 GOLD is a Croatian commercial cable television movie channel based in Zagreb, Croatia. The program is mainly produced in Croatian and Bosnian language. It is available via cable systems and IPTV platforms throughout the Bosnia and Herzegovina and Croatia. ==References== == External links == * M1 Film * M1 FILM in Facebook Category:Mass media in Sarajevo Category:Movie channels Category:Television stations in Bosnia and Herzegovina
